{"tid":2310180,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Mandy Lieu五年抱四去年再生女 同洗米華永遠係「一家人」","createTime":"2020-12-03T05:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T11:09:15.000Z","uid":212249,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"06ddd7dad85aff4464127093b13b266223cc31e3","tid":2310180,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:35:42.000Z","msg":"太陽娛樂老闆「洗米華」周焯華與Mandy Lieu的五年婚外情已玩完，外間一直傳聞兩人育有一子兩女，分手後子女跟她定居倫敦，有指Mandy拿了3億分手費，早前更斥資做億元農場女主人，成功引來英國傳媒注意。前日《Evening Standard》刊出她的大篇幅專訪，除了分享她的億萬農場的雄圖生意大計，最爆炸性的是揭露Mandy為已婚億萬大亨洗米華生下4名子女，分別是5歲的大女、4歲的二子、3歲的三女及1歲的孻女，原來她去年再為洗米華誕下孻女，而這段五年抱四的消息，直至現在才曝光。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》獨家得到一張孻女的側面相，相中B女頭髮濃密，面珠肥嘟嘟、鼻尖尖，擁有單眼皮，樣子較為似爸爸多一點。據知，Mandy 與洗米華去年已決定分手，惟分手後Mandy才發現又懷孕，而BB於去年10月出世。洗米華和Mandy育有4名子女，連同前妻所生的大仔周柏豪、現任太太陳慧玲（Heidi）所生的兩名女兒周梓童及周羨童，即共有7名子女。<br />\n<br />\n洗米華幫手睇仔女功課<br />\n<br />\n而在接受英媒訪問中，Mandy提到二人雖已分手，不過會為子女聯成一線：「With the children we are always going to be a family &mdash; he is the reasoning voice of the family, asking if they have done their homework, whereas I want to know how their sunflower seeds are doing. 」即是兩人育有子女，永遠都是一家人，還指洗米華在家裏會理性發聲，還會關心問仔女的功課。文中又以「millionaire model」來形容她的身份，她分享大女Sarah因想要一頭牛做聖誕禮物，故此她就買下農莊，開始她的億萬農場生意大計。<br />\n<br />\n而在Mandy 的網站中，她在9月曾出過一篇名為「One day everything changed」的帖文，還貼了一張捉住BB的小手相，未知是否跟孻女的牽手合照，文中更提到大女出世，令到她的人生出現重大改變。<br />\n<br />\nMandy 自從和洗米華分手後，近月在英國動作多多，轉型做才女，為雜誌做專欄作家，分享持續性健康飲食生活，全力博洗底，再斥資2億8千萬在當地漢普郡（Hampshire）購入佔地370多萬平方米的Ewhurst莊園，計劃將莊園打造成生產高品質有機食品的生態農場，<a href=\"http://及開了自己名字的mandylieu.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%8A%E9%96%8B%E4%BA%86%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E7%9A%84mandylieu.com&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=a7fbc848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">及開了自己名字的mandylieu.com</a>網站等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j0refV9ypH6JFDmNwEVQLTaDBwo=/638x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6CU7PIOZKJC6DFZTZ5I5J6LCJI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj0refV9ypH6JFDmNwEVQLTaDBwo%3D%2F638x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6CU7PIOZKJC6DFZTZ5I5J6LCJI.jpg&h=5b9cb374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eoKFywgoEYlWlT-UrnsEbmeCq5Y=/962x1600/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V7MUVKRCKVFXRLRVSNHNOUUYIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeoKFywgoEYlWlT-UrnsEbmeCq5Y%3D%2F962x1600%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV7MUVKRCKVFXRLRVSNHNOUUYIY.jpg&h=9be782a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e3a842d9d3beb44e1d1f37c5e8a66afe72125d6","tid":2310180,"uid":212249,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201203/J6GJRGH6BRD5HO65LHKZ5U43YA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201203%2FJ6GJRGH6BRD5HO65LHKZ5U43YA%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=877f224e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201203%2FJ6GJRGH6BRD5HO65LHKZ5U43YA%2F&h=7fc23b18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201203/J6GJRGH6BRD5HO65LHKZ5U43YA/</a>"},{"pid":"b0edcfc78defe4a72684ab2d93b206f90a84a1bc","tid":2310180,"uid":114721,"like":60,"dislike":2,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:42:01.000Z","msg":"請香港人做野ok?"},{"pid":"fc38f9c5266b109d06026d172ec66ed63a205728","tid":2310180,"uid":342115,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"咁屌得嘅<br />\n不過人哋有錢養 吹咩"},{"pid":"3f638a629756c6d5eed8b50502189bd8446acc15","tid":2310180,"uid":19948,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re